=0.04

* new method string2XMLObject() to pass plain XML strings
  on the stack (not intended for other strings);
	
=0.03

* empty XML tags now produced as <tag></tag>, as Opera
  and Firefox failed to handle <tag />;


=0.02

High bit characters are transformed into XML entities now.


=0.01

Initial public release. The modules were split off from the PerlPoint::Package distribution.

